cs.AI, cs.LO, cs.DB, cs.PL, cs.SE 

The paper deals with an extension of answer set programs (ASP) with external sources, which is a topic related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and logic programming (cs.LO). The paper also discusses the optimization of the evaluation algorithm, which involves database techniques (cs.DB) and programming languages (cs.PL). Finally, the paper presents experimental results and characterizations of program equivalence, which are relevant to software engineering (cs.SE).
